# Entity slugs (PK / FK)

- **`providers.slug`**, **`types.slug`**, and **`distances.slug`** are primary keys. **`races.type_slug`**, **`races.provider_slug`**, and **`race_distances.distance_slug`** reference those slugs.
- **Format** (enforced by `npm run validate-db`):
  - Lowercase ASCII letters and digits only, separated by single hyphens (kebab-case).
  - Pattern: `^[a-z0-9]+(-[a-z0-9]+)*$` — no spaces, underscores, or diacritics.
- **Stability**: Prefer stable slugs from upstream sources when they already match this format; otherwise derive by normalizing (lowercase, replace non-alphanumeric runs with `-`, collapse repeats, trim hyphens).

See `docs/slug-conventions.md` for the full reference.
